---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import { SITE_DESCRIPTION, SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
import ProfileImage from '../assets/profile.jpg';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={`关于 - ${SITE_TITLE}`} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} image={ProfileImage} />
		<style>
			.about-hero {
				display: grid;
				grid-template-columns: minmax(320px, 0.86fr) minmax(0, 1.14fr);
				gap: 1.5rem;
				align-items: start;
				padding: 1rem 0 2rem;
			}

			.portrait-panel,
			.copy-panel,
			.note-card {
				padding: 1rem;
			}

			.portrait-panel :global(img) {
				width: 100%;
				aspect-ratio: 1 / 1.16;
				object-fit: cover;
				border-radius: calc(var(--radius-xl) - 8px);
			}

			.copy-panel {
				display: grid;
				gap: 1rem;
				padding: 1.6rem;
			}

			.copy-panel p {
				max-width: 42rem;
				font-size: 1.04rem;
			}

			.info-grid {
				display: grid;
				grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
				gap: 0.9rem;
			}

			.info-card {
				padding: 1rem 1.1rem;
				border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
				background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.76);
				border: 1px solid rgba(114, 138, 123, 0.12);
			}

			.info-card span {
				display: block;
				margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
				font-size: 0.78rem;
				font-weight: 700;
				letter-spacing: 0.14em;
				text-transform: uppercase;
				color: var(--ink-faint);
			}

			.note-grid {
				display: grid;
				grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
				gap: 1rem;
			}

			.note-card {
				display: grid;
				gap: 0.7rem;
				background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.76);
				border: 1px solid rgba(114, 138, 123, 0.14);
				border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
			}

			.note-card span {
				font-size: 0.78rem;
				font-weight: 700;
				letter-spacing: 0.14em;
				text-transform: uppercase;
				color: var(--ink-faint);
			}

			.contact-link {
				display: inline-flex;
				align-items: center;
				justify-content: center;
				width: fit-content;
				padding: 0.8rem 1rem;
				border-radius: 999px;
				background: var(--accent);
				color: white;
				font-weight: 700;
				box-shadow: 0 16px 35px rgba(95, 141, 116, 0.24);
			}

			@media (max-width: 960px) {
				.about-hero,
				.note-grid {
					grid-template-columns: 1fr;
				}
			}

			@media (max-width: 720px) {
				.copy-panel {
					padding: 1.2rem;
				}

				.info-grid {
					grid-template-columns: 1fr;
				}
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<section class="about-hero">
				<div class="portrait-panel soft-panel">
					<Image src={ProfileImage} alt="sonder avatar" width={700} height={812} />
				</div>
				<div class="copy-panel soft-panel">
					<span class="section-tag">关于我</span>
					<h1>你好，我是 sonder。</h1>
					<p>这个博客是我给自己留的一块学习空间。它不追求把一切包装得很完美，而是更想把真实的理解过程、代码实践和阶段变化慢慢写清楚。</p>
					<p>我希望这里看起来足够干净、足够舒展，也保留一点个人气质。这样每次打开的时候，不会觉得是在翻模板，而像是在翻自己的成长档案。</p>
					<div class="info-grid">
						<div class="info-card">
							<span>昵称</span>
							<strong>sonder</strong>
						</div>
						<div class="info-card">
							<span>一句话</span>
							<strong>保持热爱，无限进步</strong>
						</div>
						<div class="info-card">
							<span>写作内容</span>
							<strong>学习记录 / 实践笔记 / 阶段复盘</strong>
						</div>
						<div class="info-card">
							<span>邮箱</span>
							<strong>3192422357@qq.com</strong>
						</div>
					</div>
					<a class="contact-link" href="mailto:3192422357@qq.com">给我发邮件</a>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section class="note-grid">
				<div class="note-card">
					<span>为什么写</span>
					<h3>为了让学习不只停留在“我好像懂了”</h3>
					<p>很多内容只有写出来、重组过，才算真正进入自己的理解体系。这个博客就是这个过程的一部分。</p>
				</div>
				<div class="note-card">
					<span>怎么写</span>
					<h3>尽量写具体、写过程、写卡住的地方</h3>
					<p>我会更关注真实的学习路径，而不是只保留最后那个“看起来正确”的答案。</p>
				</div>
				<div class="note-card">
					<span>我希望它变成什么</span>
					<h3>以后回来看时，能看到自己确实走远了</h3>
					<p>它既是写给别人的，也是写给未来的自己。最好几年后再翻，还能看见现在的认真。</p>
				</div>
			</section>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
